o|last=Ram\u00edrez-Mac\u00edas|first=Den\u00ed|publisher=Publicia|year=2013|isbn=978-3639551457|language=es}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Ramirez Macias, Deni}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Year of birth missing (living people)]]\n[[Category:Mexican women]]\n[[Category:Mexican scientists]]\n[[Category:Women scientists]]\n[[Category:Marine biologists]]\n", "name_user": "Leela52452", "label": "safe", "comment": "Infobox person > Infobox scientist, add: DOB. misc cosmetic changes.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Den%C3%AD_Ram%C3%ADrez_Mac%C3%ADas"}
